'''热带风暴克里斯'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Chris}}）是[[2006年大西洋飓风季|2006年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第4场[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]。系统于7月31日经[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]以东[[大西洋|大西洋]]海域的[[东风波|东风波]]发展形成，之后总体向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向前进，从[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]群岛的北侧边缘掠过。克里斯的存在周期较为短暂，于8月2日在[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]以北洋面达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时100公里的最高强度。接下来气旋逐渐减弱，于8月5日在[[古巴|古巴]]以东消散。这场风暴对陆地构成的影响很小，没有造成人员伤亡，只有沿途产生中等程度降水。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Chris 2006 track.png}}
7月27日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开[[非洲|西非]]海岸，起初其轴线周围有旺盛的[[对流|对流]]持续存在，但这些对流因受干燥空气的不利影响而于7月28日基本消亡。东风波继续西进，风场依然层次分明，轴线最北端附近在两天后已有深层对流滋长。7月30日，对流的纵向深度和组织结构都有改善，气象机构因此启动[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]对系统进行分析。7月31日，有[[浮标_(航路标识)|浮标]]测得系统风向从东北转为向西，表明已有小规模[[低气压|低气压区]]形成。系统转向西北，对流组织迅速改善，于8月1日在[[巴布达岛|巴布达岛]]东南偏东方向约375公里海域发展成[[2006年大西洋飓风季|2006年大西洋飓风季]]的第三号热带低气压。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Tropical Cyclone Report | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2010-06-16 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL032006_Chris.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100616171223/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL032006_Chris.pdf | date =  }}</ref>

气象部门起初预计上层低气压产生的[[风切变|风切变]]会阻止低气压增强，令其在3天内消散<ref name="nhcdisc1">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression Three Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.001.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114023/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。但受到中等强度风切变影响的气旋仍然在环流中心附近发展出深层对流，低气压也继续组织，仅6小时后就增强成热带风暴并获名“克里斯”（{{lang|en|Chris}}）<ref name="tcr" /><ref name="nhcdisc2">{{cite report | author = Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114038/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.002.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。对流逐渐在系统上空集中，克里斯于8月1日晚在[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]北部以北约80公里洋面经过时，风速已经达到每小时95公里<ref name="nhcdisc3">{{cite report | author = Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.006.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114044/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.006.shtml | date =  }}</ref>。风暴结构继续改善，变得更加对称，并在8月2日清晨发展出上层[[风眼|眼状特征]]。各象限的外流都在改善，<ref name="nhcdisc4">{{cite report | author = Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Seven | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114102/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2006-08-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.007.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>风暴不久后就在[[圣托马斯岛_(美属维尔京群岛)|圣托马斯岛]]以东约195公里海域达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]100公里的最高强度。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]一度预计克里斯会受[[高压脊|高压脊]]影响向西北偏西方向移动，并逐渐增强至飓风标准<ref name="nhcdisc5">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.008.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>，但风暴实际上在上层风切变的影响下导致原本层次分明的内层核心消亡，气旋开始减弱<ref name="nhcdisc6">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114104/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.009.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.009.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。

[[File:chrissplitloop.gif|250px]]影响，克里斯开始减弱]]

到了8月3日中午左右，约135公里范围的环流内已经没有任何对流，深层对流则散布到[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]和[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]各地上空<ref name="nhcdisc8">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Twelve | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114121/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.012.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.012.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。当晚，环流中心又有深层对流发展出来<ref name="nhcdisc9">{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Discussion Fourteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-10-07 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114123/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.014.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.014.shtml? | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>，但持续存在的垂直风切变仍令克里斯于8月4日降级成热带低气压。多个[[天气预报|计算机模型]]预计风切变会减少，美国国家飓风中心因此预计气旋会在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]再度强化，达到风速每小时95公里强度<ref name="nhcdisc10">{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression Chris Discussion Sixteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.016.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114143/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.discus.016.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>，但对流实际上一直都很少，克里斯于8月4日晚退化成残留低气压区<ref name="tcr" />。8月5日晚，风暴残留内的对流有所增长，气象机构认为系统有可能因外部环境变得较为有利而在墨西哥湾缓慢发展<ref name="aug5two">{{cite report | author1 = Mainelli | author2 = Bevin | year = 2006 | title = August 5 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref><ref name="aug6two">{{cite report | author = Stewart | year = 2006 | title = August 6 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。但是，系统并未重新发展，残留环流最终于8月6日在[[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]附近完全消散<ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
[[File:Chris_ISS013E62787.jpg|thumb]]拍下热带风暴克里斯的照片]]
美国国家飓风中心针对第三号热带低气压发布首份公告时，[[安提瓜和巴布达|安提瓜和巴布达]]、[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]、[[圣克里斯多福与尼维斯|圣克里斯多福与尼维斯]]和[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]政府向各自领土发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="nhcadv1">{{cite report | author = Franklin | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression Three Public Advisory One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114022/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。低气压升级成热带风暴时，[[萨巴_(荷兰)|萨巴]]、[[圣尤斯特歇斯|圣尤斯特歇斯]]、[[圣巴泰勒米|圣巴泰勒米]]和[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]也相继发布热带风暴警告<ref name="nhcadv2">{{cite report | author = Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Public Advisory Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114031/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.002.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。3艘[[皇家加勒比国际游轮|皇家加勒比国际游轮]]变更航线避开风暴<ref name="cnn">{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris loses steam | url = http://www.caribbean-on-line.com/hurricanes/archives/2006/08/tropical_storm_chris_loses_steam.html | accessdate = 2008-09-07 | archivedate = 2008-09-07 | deadurl = yes | work = caribbean-on-line.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080907143240/http://www.caribbean-on-line.com/hurricanes/archives/2006/08/tropical_storm_chris_loses_steam.html }}</ref>。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]代表同[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]地方应急管理官员协调合作，确定包括医院占用率、避难所和沙袋在内的各项资源是否足以应对风暴威胁<ref name="fema">{{cite web | author = FEMA | year = 2006 | title = National Situation Update | accessdate = 2012-07-03 | url = http://www.fema.gov/emergency/reports/2006/nat080306.shtm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120703215146/http://www.fema.gov/emergency/reports/2006/nat080306.shtm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-07-03 }}</ref>。

8月1日，[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]政府向岛上发布热带风暴警告<ref name="nhvad4">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Public Advisory Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114034/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.004.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | date =  }}</ref>。次日，约有600名游客撤离[[别克斯岛|别克斯岛]]和[[库莱布拉岛|库莱布拉岛]]<ref name="cnn" />。[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]政府也在这天向[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]、[[阿克林岛与克鲁克德岛|阿克林岛与克鲁克德岛]]、[[拉吉德岛|拉吉德岛]]、[[伊纳瓜|伊纳瓜]]和[[马亚瓜纳岛|马亚瓜纳岛]]发布飓风观察预警<ref name="nhcadv8">{{cite report | author = Pasch | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Public Advisory Eight | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002114058/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.008.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/al03/al032006.public.008.shtml? | date =  }}</ref>。面对风暴的威胁，政府敦促居民储备应急物资，斯坦尼尔礁的船主则在气旋来袭前将船只固定<ref name="cnn" />。

气象机构预计克里斯会进入墨西哥湾后，[[纽约商品期货交易所|纽约商品期货交易所]]驻伦敦分支机构的原油价格上涨<ref name="fe_oil">{{cite news | title = Oil surges as Storm Chris heads toward Gulf of Mexico | date = 2006-08-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061019005810/http://www.financialexpress.com/fe_full_story.php?content_id=136007 | deadurl = yes | publisher = Financial Express | url = http://www.financialexpress.com/fe_full_story.php?content_id=136007 | archivedate = 2006-10-19 | accessdate = 2015-11-08 }}</ref>，8月2日，纽约商品期货交易所电子交易平台的[[天然气|天然气]]价格也有大幅上涨。北美洲这时正受到[[2006年北美洲热浪|热浪]]的影响，天然气市场需求较高，对克里斯强化成飓风并威胁天然气供应的担忧导致天然气价格上涨<ref name="bloom_natgas">{{cite news |title=Natural Gas Surges in New York on Hurricane Threat, Heat Wave |date=2006-08-02 |publisher=Bloomberg |archivedate=2012-10-15 |author=Geoffrey Smith |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015021359/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=abwMe8IynKn4&refer=home |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087&sid=abwMe8IynKn4&refer=home |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-11-08 }}</ref>。[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]包括市长[[雷·纳金|雷·纳金]]（{{lang|en|Ray Nagin}}）在内的政府官员准备在克里斯以飓风强度进入墨西哥湾后疏散全城。疏散计划包括在最严峻的形势下将所有居民运出城，以免再出现约一年前[[2005年颶風卡特里娜|飓风卡特里娜]]引发的惨剧。<ref name="msnbc">{{cite news |agency=[[路透社|Reuters]] |date=2006-08-03 |newspaper=New Zealand Herald |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130223032855/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=10394343 |title=New Orleans nervously eyes tropical storm Chris |accessdate=2015-11-08 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/world/news/article.cfm?c_id=2&objectid=10394343 |archivedate=2013-02-23 }}</ref>佛罗里达州紧急事务管理局要求开设10个流动恢复中心，要求[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]的多家医院做好撤离准备。[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]官员确定，如果风暴[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，该州需要约110人协助疏散过程。[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]和[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的紧急行动中心都密切关注气旋动向，但最终都没有执行任何准备行动。<ref name="fema" />

== 影响 ==
[[File:Chris_2006_rainfall.png|thumb]]
虽然一度构成威胁，但克里斯对[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]的影响很小<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Caribbean Meteorological Organization | date = 2006-12-04 | title = Report of the Annual meeting of the Directors of Meteorological Services | accessdate = 2010-12-30 | url = http://www.cmo.org.tt/Docs/CMC46/pdfs/MET_DIRECTOR_REPORT_2006.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120314060132/http://www.cmo.org.tt/Docs/CMC46/pdfs/MET_DIRECTOR_REPORT_2006.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-03-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴总体造成的破坏很小，在波多黎各产生小雨，降雨量最高的[[法哈多|法哈多]]约为78毫米<ref name="tcr" />。这些降水导致法哈多河（{{lang|en|Fajardo River}}）泛滥，导致波多黎各东北部的一截高速公路临时封闭<ref>{{cite news |author=Miranda Leitsinger |date=2006-08-04 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130209010539/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/03/AR2006080301546.html |title=Tropical Storm Pushes Across Caribbean |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|Washington Post]] |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/03/AR2006080301546.html |accessdate=2015-11-08 |archivedate=2013-02-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]、[[特克斯和凯科斯群岛|特克斯和凯科斯群岛]]、[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]和[[古巴|古巴]]东部部分地区的降雨量达到50毫米，还有部分山区达到100毫米<ref name="zeenews">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm Chris wreaks havoc before downgrading | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070928000403/http://www.zeenews.com/znnew/articles.asp?aid=313893&ssid=26&sid=ENV | date = 2006-08-06 | url = http://www.zeenews.com/znnew/articles.asp?aid=313893&ssid=26&sid=ENV | author = Zee News | accessdate = 2007-09-28 | archivedate = 2007-09-28 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。暴雨在[[多米尼加|多米尼加共和国]]首都[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]引发严重洪灾。[[亚美利加国际机场|亚美利加国际机场]]测得127毫米降水<ref>{{cite report | author = DIRECCIóN GENERAL DE AERONáUTICA CIVIL | work = OFICINA NACIONAL DE METEOROLOGíA | title = RESUMEN TEMPORADA CICLóNICA 2006}}</ref>。洪水侵入房屋，致使多人暂时无家可归，圣多明哥附近的许多道路因洪水导致无法通行，还出现多起山体滑坡<ref name="domrep">{{cite news | author = Espacinsular | year = 2006 | title = Llueve torrencialmente y emiten alerta verde para 11 provincias por Chris | url = http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:3yBqUCZbpokJ:espacinsular.org/article.php3%3Fid_article%3D2026+Llueve+torrencialmente+y+emiten+alerta+verde+para+11+provincias+por+Chris&hl=en&lr=&client=firefox-a&strip=0 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。该国东北部还有部分稻田被洪水淹没，该国气象局向生活在该国东北部和东南部低洼地区及河流附近的居民发布洪灾警报。虽然出现洪灾，但多米尼加所受破坏很小，也没有出现人员丧生。<ref name="domrep2">{{cite news | author = Espancinsular | year = 2006 | title = "Chris" se alejó de República Dominicana pero dejó agua, inundaciones y daños menores | url = http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:nN9mdIPuGNwJ:espacinsular.org/article.php3%3Fid_article%3D2034+Chris%E2%80%9D+se+alej%C3%B3+de+Rep%C3%BAblica+Dominicana+pero+dej%C3%B3+agua,+inundaciones+y+da%C3%B1os+menores&hl=en&gl=us&ct=clnk&cd=1&client=firefox-a }}{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

